# MP 20 Light Site

Lightweight restaurant website with:

- plain HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- tiny Node backend using only built-in modules
- JSON-driven menu and contact details
- enquiry form that saves messages to `data/inquiries.json`

## Run locally

```powershell
cd C:\Users\gunik\mp20-light-site
npm start
```

Open `http://localhost:3000`

## Files to edit

- `data/site-data.json` for menu, phone, address, links, and reviews
- `public/styles.css` for colors and layout
- `public/index.html` for sections

## Hosting

This can be hosted on:

- any VPS with Node.js installed
- Windows Server with Node.js
- Azure App Service
- Render, Railway, or similar Node hosting
